<li id="cite_note-20"><b><a href="#cite_ref-20" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.rollingstone.com/nationalaffairs/index.php/2008/01/25/the-romney-whisper-mystery" class="external text" title="http://www.rollingstone.com/nationalaffairs/index.php/2008/01/25/the-romney-whisper-mystery" rel="nofollow">"The Romney Whisper Mystery"</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.rollingstone.com/nationalaffairs/index.php/2008/01/25/the-romney-whisper-mystery" class="external free" title="http://www.rollingstone.com/nationalaffairs/index.php/2008/01/25/the-romney-whisper-mystery" rel="nofollow">http://www.rollingstone.com/nationalaffairs/index.php/2008/01/25/the-romney-whisper-mystery</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=The+Romney+Whisper+Mystery&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rollingstone.com%2Fnationalaffairs%2Findex.php%2F2008%2F01%2F25%2Fthe-romney-whisper-mystery&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Sound_from_ultrasound"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
</ol>
</div>
